node.accessibility_caption: Photo by MATTY 🥾🌍 Amnesty Uk - DH00280 on March 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'BREAKING: NAZANIN BACK IN COURT NEXT SUNDAY'.

node.text:
Nazanin has been ‘freed’ but faces another charge and will back in court next Sunday. 

This is yet another example of the Iranian authorities playing cruel political games with Nazanin’s life. 

The UK government must not take this lying down.

#FreeNazanin  @amnestyuk
